<div class="com-share" data-id="12129" data-title="《撕开香蕉皮的那一刹那，他吓了一跳》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/12129/medium/12129.jpg?1436935140" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/12129.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
